# Metrics Directory
#
# This directory contains audit logs and metrics tracking for:
# - tool-usage.log: JSONL log of all tool operations
# - skill-usage.json: Aggregated skill/tool effectiveness metrics
# - rate-limits.json: Rate limit tracking for cost control
# - audit-log.jsonl: SOC2/HIPAA compliance audit trail
# - bash-audit.jsonl: All bash command executions
# - ghl-api-usage.jsonl: GoHighLevel API interaction tracking
# - hook-performance.jsonl: Hook execution performance data
#
# Retention: 90 days (configurable in hooks.yaml)
# Compression: After 30 days
# Encryption: Enabled for compliance
